data.description: Tucked away in the pristine Morning Mist community, this exquisite residence sets the standard for meticulously maintained homes. Morning Mist is a tranquil neighborhood graced with charming sidewalks, a delightful community playground, a serene common area, and a refreshing pool for your leisurely pleasure. Boasting four generously proportioned bedrooms, this home guarantees abundant space for your entire family. With two full bathrooms and an additional half bath, every convenience is just a step away. As you step inside, a grand two-story foyer welcomes you, leading to a flexible room that can serve as a tranquil sitting area or a dedicated office space. To the right, a spacious formal dining room offers ample room for hosting gatherings. The inviting living room, adorned with expansive windows that usher in natural light, sets the ideal ambiance for everyday life. The heart of this residence, the expansive kitchen, is a haven for culinary enthusiasts. It features a central island, ample countertop space, and meticulously designed cabinets. A spacious pantry ensures there's room for all your essentials, and the adjacent eat-in kitchen area offers a cozy setting for casual dining. An additional office space on the main level adds flexibility to cater to your specific needs. All the bedrooms are located upstairs. The master bedroom is generously spacious and adorned with vaulted ceilings and an ensuite bathroom. The other three bedrooms offer ample space and share a well-appointed bathroom. An upstairs laundry room adds a modern touch of convenience. The backyard is a serene oasis, enveloped by lush buffer trees, creating a private and tranquil retreat. The patio is perfect for outdoor grilling and leisure, making it an ideal spot to unwind and savor the beautiful surroundings. There is a two-car garage that easily accommodates your vehicles and offers ample storage space. This home offers both comfort and practicality. Don't miss the chance to call this immaculate Morning Mist residence your new home. Property includes a home warranty through 2027 at no additional cost and all major systems are in great condition.
